"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449255","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2016-02-24","<p>Tech North has received funding of £2m in 2015-16. In addition the 2015 Spending Review allocated funding for Tech North of £2m in 2016-17 and £2m in 2017-18. This funding is provided via Tech City UK. An annual delivery plan for Tech North, to be agreed with DCMS, will determine how its funds are spent for each year it has funding.</p>","Wantage","Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449255/answer",,,,,,"2016-02-24T13:59:38.36Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449255/answer","Biography information for Mr Edward Vaizey","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449255/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2016-02-01","Tech North: Finance","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what funding the Government plans to allocate to Tech North in (a) 2015-16, (b) 2016-17 and (c) 2017-18; and who decides on what that funding is spent.","false","Biography information for Chi Onwurah","Newcastle upon Tyne Central","Chi Onwurah","25010"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449256","Department for Business, Innovation and Skills","false","2016-02-09","<p>There is no set time limit for membership of the Apprenticeships Delivery Board, this will be reviewed by the Chair and refreshed accordingly.</p>","Grantham and Stamford","Nick Boles","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449256/answer",,,,,,"2016-02-09T17:28:13.313Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449256/answer","Biography information for Nick Boles","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449256/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2016-02-01","Apprenticeship Delivery Board: Membership","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, pursuant to the Answer of 1 February 2016 to Question 23617, what the length will be of the time limited period of membership of the Apprenticeship Delivery Board.","false","Biography information for Peter Kyle","Hove","Peter Kyle","25054"
