"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449439","Department of Health","false","2016-02-04","<p>The information is not held in the format requested.</p>","North East Bedfordshire","Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449439/answer",,,,,,"2016-02-04T17:00:05.7Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449439/answer","Biography information for Alistair Burt","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/449439/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2016-02-01","General Practitioners: Greater London","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, how many GP surgeries (a) closed, (b) opened and (c) merged in (i) London, (ii) each London borough and (iii) each Trust area in London in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Sadiq Khan","Tooting","Sadiq Khan","25159"
